snippet.title: The UNTOLD TRUTH about Johnny Depp!
snippet.description:
Hey guys, today we're looking at the UNTOLD TRUTH about Johnny Depp!

Though he's had a tortured relationship with fame, he's a master of his craft — and an extremely interesting guy to boot. We've heard no shortage of larger-than-life stories about Depp over the years, but they don't tell the whole story. Even after spending all these years in the limelight, there's still plenty that's been left out of the headlines — as he proved once again in 2018, when a shocking photo circulated seeming to show him in disturbingly poor health. We delved into that story — and so much more — to bring you the untold truth of Johnny Depp.
